{"tid":2264064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"各區開花事隔一年 四男女被控非法集結 包括12歲及14歲女學生","createTime":"2020-10-30T10:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T10:57:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb31520ae24c65e1294e73ec1bdf46e7dbd186f","tid":2264064,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"去年10月13日各區開花爭取五大訴求的「神獸罷鷲」行動，事隔一年，再有兩男兩女被控非法集結及違反蒙面法，包括兩名分別12歲及14歲的女學生。案件今在西九龍法院提堂，控方其中一名證人為飛虎隊特警，獲法庭頒令匿名保護身份，至於會否使用屏風作供及用特別通道出入法庭，則留待日後處理。<br />\n<br />\n控方為其中一名證人申請匿名令，辯方沒有反對，法庭頒令該名警署警長以「Y」作代號，至於屏風及特別通道問題容後處理。案件應辯方申請押後至12月23日再訊，各被告繼續保釋，其間兩名女生須晚9朝7宵禁，並由家長提供500元作人事擔保。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/UHTMTSWYJZGQNP77DXVHMZMD5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FUHTMTSWYJZGQNP77DXVHMZMD5A%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=f40bd3f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FUHTMTSWYJZGQNP77DXVHMZMD5A%2F&h=af0a1d08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/UHTMTSWYJZGQNP77DXVHMZMD5A/</a>"},{"pid":"2abc18829dfb6560c1983d33ff76de312b675d80","tid":2264064,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:41:18.000Z","msg":"做差佬做到咁唔得光，咪撚做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577e0e562ba258ed9d8ecbe3df137d3c50d223e5","tid":2264064,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eac05c82b9a71be615a8a7e95b70cdb618b4fd2","tid":2264064,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=